<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-08142356-baa9-491a-bbd5-5b5805c0de66'>
            
<p class="">45.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
                Mr. Platts-Mills
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister whether he is aware that a deputation representing the staff side of the Whitley Council for the Air Department has been officially informed that all work at Air Ministry Headquarters must be regarded as vital to the security of the State; that the Civil Service Clerical Association has been officially informed that it has been decided to extend this principle to all Air Ministry establishments; and why this extension of the purge of the Civil Service was not first notified to this House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-a9120c60-3a6c-4a97-a0aa-bf0df1059a46">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9 hs_ColumnNumber content-container " >
                <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-hop-debug-tooltip class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign hidden hidden-xs" data-placement="bottom" title=" hs_ColumnNumber "></span>

<p class="hs_ColumnNumber"><span id="941" class="column-number column-only" data-column-number="941"></span></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Attlee)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am aware that my right hon. Friend has ruled that all employment in the Air Ministry Headquarters establishment must be regarded as employment in connection with work the nature of which is vital to the security of the State. My right hon. Friend informs me that the statement in the second part of the Question is inaccurate. The position of Air Ministry outstations is still under consideration. I cannot accept the view that the action taken by my right hon. Friend constitutes any extension of the policy announced to the House on 15th March.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-2e961ea9-0cc7-4211-973e-58ecd5e95ee0">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
                Mr. Platts-Mills
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does my right hon. Friend say that, when he first announced to the House on 15th March the introduction of this instalment of the American way of life, the House was expected to understand that the lowest clerk or lift attendant in the Air Ministry, who has no possible contact with high grade secrets, might be exposed to victimisation?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-18875556-705f-4019-88bb-4f78419fefb5">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182">
                Mr. Ronald Chamberlain
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-06-21/debates/2aa9a8a8-37e0-4fc0-8da1-c90cbb1ae5f0/CivilService(CommunistsAndFascists)#contribution-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does not the Prime Minister agree that we are on the slippery slope and that personal liberty is being menaced, for on 15th March he talked about employment where important secret matters have to be covered, but now, in his instructions to the Advisory Committee, he talks about employment in connection with work vital to the security of the State, which is very much wider?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5d122053-1bd5-46b9-807d-98eb8d292182" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
